{"tid":1020424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為登全版廣告 自比欖球界紐西蘭","createTime":"2019-02-13T14:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:56:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68e798614c0eea2c0752e63ba203f7231de6806b","tid":1020424,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/02/13/2058350_d8cb9f92295f0b85c6b8a547566bba68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F02%2F13%2F2058350_d8cb9f92295f0b85c6b8a547566bba68.jpg&h=41f6674c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為在紐西蘭報章刊登廣告，指沒有華為的5G，有如欠缺紐西蘭的欖球界。(網上圖片)<br />\n美國拉攏英、加、澳、紐四國，擬制裁中國私人企業華為。華為今日在紐西蘭報章刊登全版廣告，寫上標語「沒有華為的5G，有如欠缺紐西蘭的欖球界」，希望在紐西蘭封鎖華為一事上，挽回公眾的信心。<br />\n<br />\n華為在《紐西蘭先驅報》(New Zealand Herald)和《Stuff》旗下報章刊登廣告，廣告並指5G能為紐西蘭提供就業及創新的機會，但若沒有華為，紐西蘭將錯失使用最先進的5G科技，消費者亦因需要付出更高的價格而蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭當局去年11月以重大國家安全風險為由，拒絕批准該國電訊公司Spark使用華為的5G設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2058350/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A+%E8%87%AA%E6%AF%94%E6%AC%96%E7%90%83%E7%95%8C%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2058350%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%2B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%25AC%2596%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=bfc06b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2058350/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A+%E8%87%AA%E6%AF%94%E6%AC%96%E7%90%83%E7%95%8C%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD</a>"},{"pid":"e5c72433c905fb043d69f1b36d634ea94caaf8ea","tid":1020424,"uid":169832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"who are we ....講， who are we .....吊"}]}